{"tid":1197593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭既回應，係對全香港以至自由世界的宣戰聲明","createTime":"2019-06-10T04:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T04:35:04.000Z","uid":64191,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a53a4da3f2a72f73e2a87bc5b477b6826aa4d0","tid":1197593,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"響新冷戰既大局底下，擁有獨特經濟、司法、國際觀地位既香港，理應係企響文明世界既一方，對抗鐵幕降下，免得變成另一個東柏林<br />\n<br />\n面對排水倒海既反對聲音，遺憾既係林鄭月娥閣揆堅持己見，甘願做北方派既陣前卒，公然挑戰香港103萬人、文明世界二十八國既擔憂與反對，更聲稱香港人唔了解、世界唔了解，堅持相信唔通過會成為逃犯天堂。<br />\n<br />\n逃犯天堂一說係表面，實際係為自己利益，堅持要斷送香港未來十個世代既希望，毀滅香港呢幾十年黎既建設與聲譽，強行拉到落後既極權世界<br />\n<br />\n誇張咁講，港府已私底下假借香港，向整個自由與文明世界宣戰了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0dd8f7c5d1d026c0ca36adffdba22ffccba4eb4","tid":1197593,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"I repeat, this is a war!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f9e99a0ea852587a35201219e98a2ade427b0c","tid":1197593,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"香港=東德"},{"pid":"e20287ad388385591cac439595d179a79272146b","tid":1197593,"uid":38535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sUFLOdK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsUFLOdK.png&h=b34d653c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4927621abaede810dc2a38ebf8cd664821d6f10","tid":1197593,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"香港即將既命運<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.zmescience.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/iron_curtain.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.zmescience.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2Firon_curtain.jpg&h=c714eca4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}